pullRequest.title: [FLINK-16364] [table] Deprecate the methods in TableEnvironment proposed by FLIP-84
pullRequest.bodyText:
What is the purpose of the change
*Flip-64 has provided ConnectTableDescriptor#createTemporaryTable to register TableSource in TableEnvironment. fromTableSource(TableSource<?>) should be deprecated.
The execution semantics of void sqlUpdate(String) method is inconsistent. DDL will be executed immediately while INSERT INTO statement will be buffered.
void sqlUpdate(String) and insertInto(String, Table) will buffer SQLs and Tables, but the buffer behavior is unclear.  there is no a clear mechanism through TableEnvironment API to control the whole flow. execute(String) method and explain(boolean) method are buffer-related method.
They should be deprecated, new methods is introduced in FLINK-16366 and FLINK-16367.
This pr aims to deprecate the methods in TableEnvironment proposed by FLIP-84, and do some code cleanup (or refactor) based on new introduced methods*
Brief change log

Deprecate TableEnvironment#fromTableSource(TableSource<?>), TableEnvironment#sqlUpdate(String), TableEnvironment#insertInto(String, Table), TableEnvironment#execute(String), TableEnvironment#explain(boolean), Table#insertInto(TableEnvironment#)
use TableEnvironment#from instead of deprecated method: TableEnvironment#scan
refactor plan verify tool based on StatementSet
use TableEnvironment#executeSql and StatementSet instead of deprecated methods: TableEnvironment#sqlUpdate and TableEnvironment#insertInto

Verifying this change
This change is a trivial rework / code cleanup without any test coverage.

commit.message:
[FLINK-16364] [table] Deprecate the methods proposed by FLIP-84,

including:
TableEnvironment.sqlUpdate(String)
TableEnvironment.insertInto(String, Table)
TableEnvironment.execute(String)
TableEnvironment.explain(boolean)
TableEnvironment.fromTableSource(TableSource<?>)
Table.insertInto(String)

please use TableEnvironment#executeSql for single statement,
use Table#executeInsert for single sink,
use TableEnvironment#createStatementSet for multiple sinks.
[FLINK-16364] [table] use TableEnvironment#from instead of deprecated method: TableEnvironment#scan
[FLINK-16364] [table] refactor plan verify tool based on StatementSet
[FLINK-16364] [table] use TableEnvironment#executeSql and StatementSet instead of deprecated methods: TableEnvironment#sqlUpdate and TableEnvironment#insertInto
address kurt's comment: deprecate TableEnvironment#explain(Table) (fix [FLINK-16364] [table] Deprecate the methods proposed by FLIP-84)
fix [FLINK-16364] [table] refactor plan verify tool based on StatementSet
[FLINK-16364] [table] use Table#explain instead of deprecated method: TableEnvironment#explain(Table) or TableEnvironment#explain(Table, Boolean)

address kurt's comments: rename syncExecuteInsert to execInsertXXAndWaitResult  (fix [FLINK-16364] [table] use TableEnvironment#executeSql and StatementSet instead of deprecated methods: TableEnvironment#sqlUpdate and TableEnvironment#insertInto)
